snippet.title: Unloved DC Part 01 - House of Memories
snippet.description:
Unloved is a GZDoom mapset I released in early 2010. Special thanks to Hippocat who requested me to do a playthrough of this. A lot of people say that this is one of the hardest mods for Doom2, so maybe it will be a bit interesting for some people  to see the creator play his own stuff.

Unloved: http://www.doomworld.com/idgames/index.php?id=16060
Beautiful Doom: http://www.doomworld.com/idgames/index.php?id=15965

Check out Hippocat for very cool and funny lets plays at http://www.youtube.com/user/hipp0cat

Like action packed zombie apocalypse sidescrollers? Check out my freeware game at www.gungirl2.com
